{"tid":1262184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】保皇黨提休會辯論後投棄權票 中環(駐港解放軍)軍事碼頭附屬法例周六自動生效","createTime":"2019-06-27T14:48:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T07:47:20.000Z","uid":259088,"like":2,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"debdb5ed5dced57beaa29e0fea93b69a366d2a6f","tid":1262184,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T14:48:33.000Z","msg":"班賣港賊想搞沉香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經民聯張華峰周三於立法會突然提出休會辯論，指近日發生的「送中條例」爭議，聲稱希望討論如何解決當前社會撕裂，圖將「先訂立、後審議」、將中環海濱部份用地撥予駐港解放軍可在毋須討論的情況下自動通過。立法會今晚進行表決，結果建制派在會上「拉布」後投棄權票，最終議案在0票支持、17票反對下被否決，但因立法會大會就此表決後即告休會，變相也無法審議有關中環軍用碼頭的五條附屬法例，由於附例屬「先訂立、後審議」，換言之法例將於周六（29日）自動生效，佔地0.3公頃的中環軍用碼頭將撥予駐港解放軍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190627/59764861\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190627%2F59764861&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPLtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=229f790e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190627%2F59764861&h=884becf4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190627/59764861</a>"},{"pid":"50c9e6ef7dc4dbd1b347362f224f4190be1787af","tid":1262184,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T14:56:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53a4cea680d90c82470a21391dc11a90662a61bc","tid":1262184,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T14:58:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3d86dfb283c8eca710709cfb53bcf2d4582ef1","tid":1262184,"uid":259088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:00:59.000Z","msg":"推比所有人知道"},{"pid":"2178151d84cab7e7279150d3e1b213